snippet.title: Meet Avadh Ojha Sir | Episode 70
snippet.description:
YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/@RAYAvadhOjha

Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

snippet.title: 1st Test - Day 1 | Hindi | Key Moments | India Tour Of Bangladesh | 14th December 2022
snippet.description:
In the 1st Test match, India won the toss and elected to bat first. Both the openers were dismissed quickly but next up was Cheteshwar Pujara, who played a solid knock of 90 runs. Later, Shreyas Iyer joined the party by scoring an unbeaten 82. India ended up with 278 runs at the end of day 1 but lost 6 wickets in the process.
.
.

snippet.title: BB Ki Vines Productions- Taaza Khabar | Hotstar Specials | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Jaadu ya chamatkaar? Dhoka ya yaqeen? Vardaan ya shraap? 
Dekho Vasya ki anokhi kahani Hotstar Specials Taaza Khabar mein, all episodes streaming from Jan 6th, only on Disney+ Hotstar.

Disney+ Hotstar‚Äôs upcoming fantasy-drama series, Hotstar Specials presents Taaza Khabar explores just this with the one of India‚Äôs most beloved content creator, Bhuvan Bam in the lead. Set in Mumbai, this one-of-a-kind uplifting series will take viewers on a riveting ride of a man stumbling upon a miracle and the ripples it creates in his humble life. 

The series is being directed by Himank Gaur who previously directed Dhindora and is produced by Rohit Raj & Bhuvan Bam under the banner of BB Ki Vines Productions. The show has been penned by powerful writer duo Hussain Dalal & Abbas Dalal and also stars Shriya Pilgaonkar, JD Chakravarthy, Deven Bhojani, Prathmesh Parab, Shilpa Shukla, Mahesh Manjarekar and Nitya Mathur in pivotal roles.
 
Based on the life of a sanitation worker, the series light-heartedly depicts class-based poverty and the human desire to lead a better life. The Hotstar Specials series marks Bhuvan Bam‚Äôs first association with a streaming platform and will see him in an all-new fictional role.

#TaazaKhabarOnHotstar #BBKiVinesProductions #BhuvanBam

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Argentina 3:0 Croatia - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Argentina booked their place in the Final with a 3-0 win over Croatia at the Lusail Stadium.

Quickfire first-half goals by Lionel Messi, from the penalty spot & then from Julian Alvarez, following a darting run from his own half, put the Albiceleste in control of the contest.

The pair were at it in the second half again with Messi, after a darting run, setting up an easy tap-in for Alvarez; thus confirming a sixth #FIFAWorldCup Final appearance for the Albiceleste.

Lionel Scaloni's side will face defending champions France or surprise package Morocco in the summit clash on Sunday - Dec 18.

Enjoy the highlights of #ARGCRO & keep watching the #WorldsGreatestShow on #JioCinema & #Sports18 üì∫üì≤

snippet.title: 3 BIG FISH FRY | Streaked Spanish Mackerel Fish Fry Recipe Cooking In Village Vanjaram Meen Varuval
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook three big fish fry recipe. We call this fish as vanjaram in our village. We cutting the fish slice and marinate the slices with traditional hand-ground masala. Then we fried it in traditionally made gingelly oil.

Finally, we taste this fish fry recipe with our favorite mutton curry.

Yummy!

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3641 - Bhide Scares Dr Haathi's Patient?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | ‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: 3rd ODI | Key Moments | India Tour Of Bangladesh | 10th December 2022
snippet.description:
In the 3rd ODI, India was simply brilliant with the bat. Ishan Kishan led the side with a record-breaking double century whereas Virat Kohli scored his 72nd ton to help India reach 409 runs. Bangladesh never looked like chasing down the total as they lost wickets at crucial intervals. India ended a superb ODI series with a sizzling 227 run victory. 
.
.

snippet.description:
Hello everyone!
We are back with yet another mind blowing character ‚ÄúAjju Almari‚Äù (The Palaan).
This character has his Unique style, Attitude and He has his own funny English, which also make him hilarious üòÇ. 
As you know there will always be a tough guy in your locality or area with some of his boys and tries to be the leader of the society and wants everyone to seek help from him, for all kind of problems and he does the settlements. ‚ÄúAjju Almari‚Äù show up as he can do anything and anytime but the things turn different and that is where the rib tickling comedy isü§£. 
He always share his dramatic stories with his boys and tries to grab their attention as a BHAI of the area. 
He has an uncle who is also a tough man in the locality who supports him.
He gets a settlement matter and he unknowingly try to make Hungama in other street where he and his boys gets scolded by our ‚ÄúKiraak Khala‚Äù and as you guys know ‚ÄúKiraak Khala‚Äù doesn‚Äôt care whoever it may beüòÇ.

snippet.title: Match Highlights - France 2:0 Morocco - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
France became the first team since 1998 to stand a chance of defending their #FIFAWorldCup crown with a 2-0 win over Morocco. 

Theo Hernandez fired Les Bleus ahead in the 5th minute with an acrobatic strike. This was the first time an opposition player scored against the North Africans in #Qatar2022. The Moroccan attack tested Hugo Lloris but were unlucky to not be level. Meanwhile, Olivier Giroud could not convert two opportunities to seal the result in favour of Didier Deschamps' side.

Substitute Randal Kolo Muani scored the second of the night for the defending champions with his first touch of the ball in the 79th minute. With his first international goal, the Eintracht Frankfurt booked the dream date with Argentina & end Morocco's dream run at the #WorldsGreatestShow.

Relive the best moments from #FRAMAR and stay tuned to #JioCinema & #Sports18  to find out which nation becomes the World Champion üì∫üì≤

#Ikka #DinoJames #Badshah

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Lyrics 

[Intro: Ikka]

Hum to doobe hain
Unki tasveeron me mile sukoon nahi
Unke bin nindon me
Kya yaad mujhe bhi karti hogi woh?
Kya yaad mujhe bhi karti hogi woh?

[Chorus: Ikka]
Hum to doobe hain
Unki tasveeron me mile sukoon nahi
Unke bin nindon me
Kya yaad mujhe bhi karti hogi woh?
Kya yaad mujhe bhi karti hogi woh?

Ab uska pata nahi
Dil me jo rehta tha uski baaton ke

Kya yaad mujhe bhi karti hogi woh?

Kaafi saara kehna, par pta nhi tu kahan hai
Jaise miss mai karu, baby you miss me kya?
Mere b'day m–µ beta tune wish nahi kiya
Dino Strong hai bta, ye tujh–µ kisne kaha

Kya purane apni chats ko tu karti hogi read
Kya tu type karke messages karti hogi delete

Hum to doobe hain
Unki tasveeron me mile sukoon nahi
Unke bin nindon me
Kya yaad mujhe bhi karti hogi woh?
Kya yaad mujhe bhi karti hogi woh?

Khayal tera dil se mitaya nahi abhi
Tu gayi phir dil ye lagaya nahi kabhi
Bewafa maine tujhko bhulaya nahi abhi
Pyaar kiya bas tujhe ginwaya nahi kabhi
Bas gini barsaate or tere diye gam
Dil maane na ye baat ki ab sath nahi hum

Mere sath kaali raat or ek puri bottle Rum

Galat bas hum woh to ladki hai to sahi hai

[Chorus: Ikka]

Hum to doobe hain
Unki tasveeron me mile sukoon nahi
Unke bin nindon me
Kya yaad mujhe bhi karti hogi woh?
Kya yaad mujhe bhi karti hogi woh?

[Verse 3: Badshah]

Yeah, jo dikhe na vo dard nahi kya?
Mahol ye sard nahi kya?
Aansun na dekhe aankhein hai kiski
Jo rota hai vo mard nahi kya?
Ye bata mujhe ki kon nahi rota
Main hamare kamre me nahi sota
Light band TV on nahi hota
Main hu old school mujhse move on nahi hota
Jaane woh kaha gyi
Pehle bhi lade hai ye pehli dafa nahi
Par kabhi aisi hui woh khafa nahi
Galti hai meri, woh bewafa nahi (Woh bewafa nahi)
Maine aisa kyu kiya
Pichle mahine cancel har show kiya
Kal flight me yuhi bethe bethe ro diya
Tere jane pe pata chala maine kya kho diya

Episode 3641: 
--------------------------------------------------------
Even after failing to locate Popatlal anywhere, Bhide hasn't stopped up looking for him. Popatlal receives a rebuke from Taarak for the action he made by visiting Vidhya's home despite being specifically instructed not to. Popat requests Taarak's assistance one final time in order to find a spot to hide where Bhide won't discover him. Taarak assists Popatlal while straying Bhide from the confines of society. Popatlal is trying to locate a spot to hide, but he is unsuccessful. Bhide has now arrived at Dr. Hathi's residence to request Popatlal. Watch the episode

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3639 - 12 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3639
--------------------------------------------------------
Gogi and Goli are worried for Popatlal as he tries to hide from Bhide and his family. Bhide is furious with him and so Popatlal locks himself up on his balcony. Bhide goes to Iyer to know about the whereabouts of Popat but the Iyer couple has no clue. Gogi and Goli feel guilty for keeping Snu in the dark through all of this as Sonu rushes to her home panicked. Later on, Bhide locks up Popat's house and Popat emerges from Iyer's house. Watch the full episode to know more.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3639, 12 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Gogi and Goli are worried for Popatlal as he tries to hide from Bhide and his family. Bhide is furious with him and so Popatlal locks himself up on his balcony. Bhide goes to Iyer to know about the whereabouts of Popat but the Iyer couple has no clue. Gogi and Goli feel guilty for keeping Snu in the dark through all of this as Sonu rushes to her home panicked. Later on, Bhide locks up Popat's house and Popat emerges from Iyer's house. Watch the full episode to know more.

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:
Former crime branch officer Ketan makes a video call to show Abhijeet his new farmhouse. Suddenly Ketan gets stabbed and dies. Meanwhile, the CID team finds another body in an unidentified state of crime branch officer Maheen. Abhijeet shares his experience working a case with Ketan, Meehan, and Purvi four years ago. Is there any connection between the old case and the crime? What is it? Watch the full episode now! 

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
‚Ä¢ Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
‚Ä¢ Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
‚Ä¢ Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
‚Ä¢ Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
‚Ä¢ Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
‚Ä¢ Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
‚Ä¢ Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
‚Ä¢ Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode No: 1465
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #‡§∏‡•Ä‡§Ü‡§à‡§°‡•Ä #CID2022 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime

About CID: 
----------------- 
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: Falling for A 32 Year Old Female Ft. Shreya Gupto, Usmaan | Hasley India | Web Series | Side By Side
snippet.description:
Download the inDrive app - https://share.indrive.com/lhG6/sideby...

A mature relationship is when two partners are completely involved in their relationships and when they completely care about one another.
Relationships do not have anything to do with the differences, be it caste, religion or age.
Wo kehte hain na ki Jab Pyaar Kiya toh Darna Kya! Exactly society ke banaye gaye norms aur stereotypes ko todkar Rachit aur Prerna ne kiya hai ek example set!
Rachit is 22 and Prerna is 32, an age gap of 10 years still together promising to be with each other in all the phases of life.
Lekin Inke relationship mei bhi kuch problems hain jinko overcome karna asaan nahi hai, kya ye dono side by side rehkar nibha paayenge ek dusre ka saath?
Janne ke liye episode ko end tak dekhein!

About me:

The smallest countryside, a beautiful childhood was my past. It is a glorious experience but remains like the memory of a past life.
Due to an endless wish, persistent effort, and a grateful companionship with my better half, I was able to create my little Brindavan in the outskirts of Hyderabad just as I dreamed.
We do not know if it was our mindset, but we managed to create Patnam lo Palleturu- Our little long lost village in the city. 
We believe in living life and not in just Surviving.

I have come forward to have fun with you in a world of small and beautiful dreams.
This includes our home, beautiful garden, our Grandparents' food recipes, health tips, modern steps and the desire to share my thoughts with you.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Farq Episode 14 - [Eng Sub]- Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 13th December 2022 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Faysal Quraishi as Kamal Hassan

Sohail Sameer as Rashid

Aadi Khan as Mani
Farah Nadir as Razia

Siyani Episode 122 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 13th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran‚Äôs mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter‚Äôs nature and doesn‚Äôt stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran‚Äôs family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Neha and Sankar continue to harass Thapki with the help of black magic. Elsewhere, the Pandeys get together in the hope of Bihaan's selection in the quiz competition. Later, the Pandey family is stunned by Thapki's weird behavior.

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?
